    {
      "id": "1052f945-752d-4d25-9943-01718e0dfbc2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors propose a new deep learning model to predict student performance using the sequential aspect of interaction logs between a student and an LMS in the hopes of providing support as early as possible. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1052f945-752d-4d25-9943-01718e0dfbc2",
        "parent": {
