    {
      "id": "df981193-ca6e-45fd-9163-6a9025e166b9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors use OULAD to perform multiple early classification tasks and their proposed model achieves, at the very least, 76% when performing early prediction. When comparing the performance of the Transformer-Encoder model, the authors found that their proposed method outperformed the baselkine LSTM models by 3% to 7% on F1-Score.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "df981193-ca6e-45fd-9163-6a9025e166b9",
        "parent": {
