    {
      "id": "57e93ae0-a2ed-4280-9942-2ccf89c774f4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors also test the effect of different pre-processing options such as positional encoding. In OULAD, the best options had no positional encoding and, in some cases, worked better with weeky feature aggragation and weighted loss functions.",
